OL,3,CNet migration to UK halved in previous
OL,4,Cyear, figures show
OL,6,FThe latest decrease is the largest
OL,7,Fnumerical drop for any 12-month period
OL,8,Fand the ONS said the decline has been
OL,9,Fdriven by falling numbers of people
OL,10,Fcoming to work and study in the UK.
OL,12,FDirector of population statistics at
OL,13,Fthe ONS Mary Gregory said: "Our
OL,14,Fprovisional estimates show net
OL,15,Fmigration has almost halved compared
OL,16,Fwith the previous year, driven by
OL,17,Ffalling numbers of people coming to
OL,18,Fwork and study, particularly student
OL,19,Fdependants. This follows policy
OL,20,Fchanges brought in restricting visa
OL,21,Fapplications.
