OL,6,F"There has also been an increase in
OL,7,Femigration over the 12 months to
OL,8,FDecember 2024, especially people
OL,9,Fleaving who originally came on study
OL,10,Fvisas once pandemic travel
OL,11,Frestrictions to the UK were eased."
OL,13,FThe previous Conservative government
OL,14,Fintroduced tougher restrictions on
OL,15,Fpeople eligible to travel to the UK on
OL,16,Fwork and study visas - including a ban
OL,17,Fon foreign students and care workers
OL,18,Fbringing dependants, and a hike in the
OL,19,Fminimum salary threshold required to
OL,20,Fapply.
